item.description:
It's bluegrass night at Providence's premiere dive bar nestled in the Jewelry District. Nick a Nees is known for its rotating live music acts and for not having a cover.

It's been a while since we've checked out some live music, so what better way to beat the midweek blues than with some live bluegrass?

If you haven't been to a meetup before, this should be a fun way to meet some new folk and check out some music.

Come on down, come and go anytime and enjoy the show.

Remember, there's no cover. See you there.
item.how_to_find_us: Look kkfor us, we should be easy to find
item.name: Blugrass Throedown @ Nick a Nees
